org.eclipse.papyrus.MARTE.MARTE_DesignModel.GCM

Interface ClientServerPort

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ClientServerPortImpl

    public interface ClientServerPort
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject
    A representation of the model object 'Client Server Port'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Base Port
    • Specification Kind
    • Kind
    • Prov Interface
    • Req Interface
    • Features Spec
    See Also:
    GCMPackage.getClientServerPort()
